    fr: "Un nouveau collègue est arrivé dans notre entreprise. Il s'appelle Zhang, très grand. Il parle trois langues. Tout le monde le trouve intéressant.",
    en: "A new colleague arrived at our company. His surname is Zhang, very tall. He can speak three languages. Everyone thinks he's interesting."
